      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented test suite; all regression tests passing for ANSYS Fluent 2022R2.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022R2) is under formal version control with a documented regression test suite. All relevant solver tests passed prior to simulation execution. SQA documentation reviewed and archived."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
